                       FontSize="16" 
                       FontAttributes="Bold"/>
                    <Label Text="Our Service does not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from anyone under the age of 13. If You are a parent or guardian and You are aware that Your child has provided Us with Personal Data, please contact Us." 
                       FontSize="14"/>

                    <!-- Links to Other Websites -->
